The Nigerian Football Federation has released a 24-man list for the AFCON 2022 qualifiers against Benin Republic and Lesotho. Six players were put on stand-by for the ties.  M. OKOYE F. UZOHO J. NOBBLE W. EKONG K. OMERUO L. BALOGUN C. AWAZIEM J. COLLINS Z. SANUSI 0. AINA T. EBUEHI W. NDIDI 0. ETEBO S. AJAYI S. ABDULLAHI J. ARIBO A. MUSA M. SIMON A. IWOBI S. KALU V. OSIMHEN K. IHEANACHO S. CHUKWUEZE S. UMAR AKPEYI. ONUACHU. MOFFI. ONYEKURU. OLISE. OLAYINKA. ADELEKE 